          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3">Quality Craftsmanship</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            We use only premium 4,000+ PSI concrete with proper reinforcement. Every project is built to last 30+ years in Florida's demanding climate. No shortcuts, no compromises.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300 border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-primary/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 9V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2m2 4h10a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H9a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm7-5a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path></svg>
          </div>
